|7月5日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} )). * {{ill|Kansei|ja|Kansei|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1790 AD|ja|1790th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|July 6|ja|7月6日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – The Kansei Prohibition on Heterodox Learning was enacted, with {{ill|Matsudaira Sadanobu|ja|松平定信|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} banning the teaching of subjects other than {{ill|Neo-Confucianism|ja|朱子学|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} at {{ill|Yushima Seidō|ja|湯島聖堂|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
