'''May 24''' is the 24th day of month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|qq=|12=draft}}  the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft}}  day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|qq=|12=draft}} . 

== Events ==
* {{ill|Emperor Monmu|ja|文武天皇|qq=|12=draft}}  3rd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|699 AD|ja|699th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|June 26|ja|6月26日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – The founder of Shugendō, {{ill|En no Ozunu|ja|役行者|lt=En no Ozunu|lt_ja=役小角|qq=|12=draft}} , was exiled to {{ill|Izu Province|ja|Izu Province|lt=Izu|lt_ja=伊豆|qq=|12=draft}}  due to slander from his disciples.
* {{ill|Bunji|ja|文治|qq=|12=draft}}  1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1185 AD|ja|1185th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|June 23|ja|6月23日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – To appease {{ill|Minamoto no Yoritomo|ja|源頼朝|qq=|12=draft}} , {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshitsune|ja|源義経|lt=Yoshitsune|lt_ja=義経|qq=|12=draft}} , who was en route to Kamakura, was detained at {{ill|Koshigoe|ja|腰越|qq=|12=draft}} , and thus entrusted a letter (the {{ill|Koshigoe Letter|ja|腰越状|qq=|12=draft}} ) to {{ill|Ōe Hiromoto|ja|大江広元|qq=|12=draft}} .
* {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|12=draft}}  4th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1576 AD|ja|1576th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|June 20|ja|6月20日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Maeda Toshiie|ja|Maeda Toshiie|qq=|12=draft}}  executed approximately 1,000 captives of the {{ill|Echizen Ikko-ikki|ja|越前一向一揆|qq=|12=draft}} , subjecting them to crucifixion and boiling. (Dating based on Ikko-ikki inscription tiles is approximate; some sources propose Tenshō 8 ({{ill|1580 AD|ja|1580th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|July 5|ja|7月5日|qq=|12=draft}} )).
* {{ill|Kansei|ja|Kansei|qq=|12=draft}}  2nd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1790 AD|ja|1790th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|July 6|ja|7月6日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – The Kansei Prohibition on Heterodox Learning was enacted, with {{ill|Matsudaira Sadanobu|ja|松平定信|qq=|12=draft}}  banning the teaching of subjects other than {{ill|Neo-Confucianism|ja|朱子学|qq=|12=draft}}  at {{ill|Yushima Seidō|ja|湯島聖堂|qq=|12=draft}} .

== Births ==
* {{ill|Tenryaku|ja|天暦|qq=|12=draft}}  4th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|950 AD|ja|950th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|June 12|ja|6月12日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Reisō|ja|冷泉天皇|qq=|12=draft}} , the 63rd {{ill|Emperor|ja|天皇|qq=|12=draft}}  (d. {{ill|1011 AD|ja|1011th year|qq=|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Gennin|ja|元永|qq=|12=draft}}  1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1118 AD|ja|1118th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|June 14|ja|6月14日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Chiba Tsunetane|ja|千葉常胤|qq=|12=draft}} , a military commander and protector (shugo) of {{ill|Shimōsa Province|ja|下総国|lt=Shimōsa|qq=|12=draft}}  (d. {{ill|1201 AD|ja|1201st year|qq=|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Shōhō|ja|正保|qq=|12=draft}}  1st Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1644 AD|ja|1644th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|June 28|ja|6月28日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Tsunashige|ja|徳川綱重|qq=|12=draft}} , the first lord of the {{ill|Kōfu Domain|ja|甲府藩|qq=|12=draft}} , the third son of {{ill|Tokugawa Iemitsu|ja|徳川家光|qq=|12=draft}} , and the father of {{ill|Tokugawa Ienobu|ja|徳川家宣|qq=|12=draft}}  (d. {{ill|1678 AD|ja|1678th year|qq=|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Kōka|ja|弘化|qq=|12=draft}}  3rd Year (leap May) ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1846 AD|ja|1846th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|July 17|ja|7月17日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Iemoto|ja|徳川家茂|qq=|12=draft}} , the 14th shogun of the {{ill|Edo Shogunate|ja|Tokugawa shogunate|qq=|12=draft}}  (d. {{ill|1866 AD|ja|1866th year|qq=|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|12=draft}}  4th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1871 AD|ja|1871st year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|July 11|ja|7月11日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Kida Sadakichi|ja|喜田貞吉|qq=|12=draft}} , a historian (d. {{ill|1939 AD|ja|1939th year|qq=|12=draft}} ).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=|12=draft}}  13th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1636 AD|ja|1636th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|June 27|ja|6月27日|qq=|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Date Masamune|ja|伊達政宗|qq=|12=draft}} , a military commander and the first lord of the {{ill|Sendai Domain|ja|仙台藩|qq=|12=draft}}  (born {{ill|1567 AD|ja|1567th year|qq=|12=draft}} ).

