endar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1644 AD|ja|1644th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1644 AD|qq=}} {{ill|June 28|ja|6月28日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 28|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Tsunashige|ja|徳川綱重|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Tsunashige|qq=}} , the first lord of the {{ill|Kōfu Domain|ja|甲府藩|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōfu Domain|qq=}} , the third son of {{ill|Tokugawa Iemitsu|ja|徳川家光|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Iemitsu|qq=}} , and the father of {{ill|Tokugawa Ienobu|ja|徳川家宣|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Ienobu|qq=}} (d. {{ill|1678 AD|ja|1678th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1678 AD|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Kōka|ja|弘化|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōka|qq=}} 3rd Year (leap May) ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1846 AD|ja|1846th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1846 AD|qq=}} {{ill|July 17|ja|7月17日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 17|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Iemoto|ja|徳川家茂|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Iemoto|qq=}} , the 14th shogun of the {{ill|Edo Shogunate|ja|Tokugawa shogunate|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Edo Shogunate|qq=}} (d. {{ill|1866 AD|ja|1866th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1866 AD|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} 4th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1871 AD|ja|1871st year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1871 AD|qq=}} {{ill|July 11|ja|7月11日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 11|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Kida Sadakichi|ja|喜田貞吉|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kida Sadakichi|qq=}} , a historian (d. {{ill|1939 AD|ja|1939th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1939 AD|qq=}} ).
