{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=五月廿四|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 5월 24일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar May|qq=}} '''May 24''' is the 24th day of month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May (Lunisolar)|qq=}} the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Butsumetsu|qq=}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Emperor Monmu|ja|文武天皇|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Monmu|qq=}} 3rd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|699 AD|ja|699th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/699 AD|qq=}} {{ill|June 26|ja|6月26日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 26|qq=}} ) – The founder of Shugendō, {{ill|En no Ozunu|ja|役行者|lt=En no Ozunu|lt_ja=役小角|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/En no Ozunu|qq=}} , was exiled to {{ill|Izu Province|ja|Izu Province|lt=Izu|lt_ja=伊豆|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Izu Province|qq=}} due to slander from his disciples. * {{ill|Bunji|ja|文治|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunji|qq=}} 1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1185 AD|ja|1185th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1185 AD|qq=}} {{ill|June 23|ja|6月23日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 23|qq=}} ) – To appease {{ill|Minamoto no Yoritomo|ja|源頼朝|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minamoto no Yoritomo|qq=}} , {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshitsune|ja|源義経|lt=Yoshitsune|lt_ja=義経|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minamoto no Yoshitsune|qq=}} , who was en route to Kamakura, was detained at {{ill|Koshigoe|ja|腰越|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Koshigoe|qq=}} , and thus entrusted a letter (the {{ill|Koshigoe Letter|ja|腰越状|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Koshigoe Letter|qq=}} ) to {{ill|Ōe Hiromoto|ja|大江広元|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōe Hiromoto|qq=}} . * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō (Momoyama period)|qq=}} 4th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1576 AD|ja|1576th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1576 AD|qq=}} {{ill|June 20|ja|6月20日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 20|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Maeda Toshiie|ja|Maeda Toshiie|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Maeda Toshiie|qq=}} executed approximately 1,000 captives of the {{ill|Echizen Ikko-ikki|ja|越前一向一揆|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Echizen Ikko-ikki|qq=}} , subjecting them to crucifixion and boiling. (Dating based on Ikko-ikki inscription tiles is approximate; some sources propose Tenshō 8 ({{ill|1580 AD|ja|1580th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1580 AD|qq=}} {{ill|July 5|ja|7月5日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 5|qq=}} )). * {{ill|Kansei|ja|Kansei|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kansei|qq=}} 2nd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1790 AD|ja|1790th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1790 AD|qq=}} {{ill|July 6|ja|7月6日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 6|qq=}} ) – The Kansei Prohibition on Heterodox Learning was enacted, with {{ill|Matsudaira Sadanobu|ja|松平定信|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Matsudaira Sadanobu|qq=}} banning the teaching of subjects other than {{ill|Neo-Confucianism|ja|朱子学|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Neo-Confucianism|qq=}} at {{ill|Yushima Seidō|ja|湯島聖堂|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yushima Seidō|qq=}} .
