{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=五月廿四|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 5월 24일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar May|qq=}} '''May 24''' is the 24th day of month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May (Lunisolar)|qq=}} the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Butsumetsu|ja|仏滅|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Butsumetsu|qq=}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Emperor Monmu|ja|文武天皇|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Monmu|qq=}} 3rd Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|699 AD|ja|699年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/699 AD|qq=}} {{ill|June 26|ja|6月26日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 26|qq=}} ) – The founder of Shugendō, {{ill|En no Ozunu|ja|役行者|lt=En no Ozunu|lt_ja=役小角|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/En no Ozunu|qq=}} , was exiled to {{ill|Izu Province|ja|Izu Province|lt=Izu|lt_ja=伊豆|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Izu Province|qq=}} due to slander from his disciples. * {{ill|Bunji|ja|文治|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunji|qq=}} 1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1185 AD|ja|1185年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1185 AD|qq=}} {{ill|June 23|ja|6月23日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 23|qq=}} ) – To appease {{ill|Minamoto no Yoritomo|ja|源頼朝|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minamoto no Yoritomo|qq=}} , {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshitsune|ja|源義経|lt=Yoshitsune|lt_ja=義経|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minamoto no Yoshitsune|qq=}} , who was en route to Kamakura, was detained at {{ill|Koshigoe|ja|腰越|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Koshigoe|qq=}} , and thus entrusted a letter (the {{ill|Koshigoe Letter|ja|腰越状|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Koshigoe Letter|qq=}} ) to {{ill|Ōe Hiromoto|ja|大江広元|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōe Hiromoto|qq=}} . * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō (Momoyama period)|qq=}} 4th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1576 AD|ja|1576年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1576 AD|qq=}} {{ill|June 20|ja|6月20日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 20|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Maeda Toshiie|ja|Maeda Toshiie|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Maeda Toshiie|qq=}} executed approximately 1,000 captives of the {{ill|Echizen Ikko-ikki|ja|越前一向一揆|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Echizen Ikko-ikki|qq=}} , subjecting them to crucifixion and boiling. (Dating based on Ikko-ikki inscription tiles is approximate; some sources propose Tenshō 8 ({{ill|1580 AD|ja|1580年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1580 AD|qq=}} {{ill|July 5|ja|7月5日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 5|qq=}} )). * {{ill|Kansei|ja|Kansei|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kansei|qq=}} 2nd Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1790 AD|ja|1790年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1790 AD|qq=}} {{ill|July 6|ja|7月6日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 6|qq=}} ) – The Kansei Prohibition on Heterodox Learning was enacted, with {{ill|Matsudaira Sadanobu|ja|松平定信|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Matsudaira Sadanobu|qq=}} banning the teaching of subjects other than {{ill|Neo-Confucianism|ja|朱子学|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Neo-Confucianism|qq=}} at {{ill|Yushima Seidō|ja|湯島聖堂|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yushima Seidō|qq=}} .
== Births == * {{ill|Tenryaku|ja|天暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenryaku|qq=}} 4th Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|950 AD|ja|950年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/950 AD|qq=}} {{ill|June 12|ja|6月12日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 12|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Reisō|ja|冷泉天皇|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Reisō|qq=}} , the 63rd {{ill|Emperor|ja|天皇|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor|qq=}} (d. {{ill|1011 AD|ja|1011年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1011 AD|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Gennin|ja|元永|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gennin|qq=}} 1st Year ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1118 AD|ja|1118年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1118 AD|qq=}} {{ill|June 14|ja|6月14日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 14|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Chiba Tsunetane|ja|千葉常胤|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chiba Tsunetane|qq=}} , a military commander and protector (shugo) of {{ill|Shimōsa Province|ja|下総国|lt=Shimōsa|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shimōsa Province|qq=}} (d. {{ill|1201 AD|ja|1201年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1201 AD|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Shōhō|ja|正保|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōhō|qq=}} 1st Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1644 AD|ja|1644年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1644 AD|qq=}} {{ill|June 28|ja|6月28日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 28|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Tsunashige|ja|徳川綱重|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Tsunashige|qq=}} , the first lord of the {{ill|Kōfu Domain|ja|甲府藩|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōfu Domain|qq=}} , the third son of {{ill|Tokugawa Iemitsu|ja|徳川家光|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Iemitsu|qq=}} , and the father of {{ill|Tokugawa Ienobu|ja|徳川家宣|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Ienobu|qq=}} (d. {{ill|1678 AD|ja|1678年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1678 AD|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Kōka|ja|弘化|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōka|qq=}} 3rd Year (leap May) ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1846 AD|ja|1846年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1846 AD|qq=}} {{ill|July 17|ja|7月17日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 17|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Iemoto|ja|徳川家茂|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Iemoto|qq=}} , the 14th shogun of the {{ill|Edo Shogunate|ja|Tokugawa shogunate|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Edo Shogunate|qq=}} (d. {{ill|1866 AD|ja|1866年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1866 AD|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} 4th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1871 AD|ja|1871年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1871 AD|qq=}} {{ill|July 11|ja|7月11日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/July 11|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Kida Sadakichi|ja|喜田貞吉|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kida Sadakichi|qq=}} , a historian (d. {{ill|1939 AD|ja|1939年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1939 AD|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kan'ei|qq=}} 13th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1636 AD|ja|1636年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1636 AD|qq=}} {{ill|June 27|ja|6月27日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 27|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Date Masamune|ja|伊達政宗|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Date Masamune|qq=}} , a military commander and the first lord of the {{ill|Sendai Domain|ja|仙台藩|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sendai Domain|qq=}} (born {{ill|1567 AD|ja|1567年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1567 AD|qq=}} ).
