rian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1846|en|1846|qid=Q7640|lt=1846 AD|1=1846}} {{ill|July 17|en|July 17|qid=Q2729|lt=July 17|1=July 17}} ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Iemochi|en|Tokugawa Iemochi|qid=Q348466|lt=Tokugawa Iemoto|1=Tokugawa Iemochi}} , the 14th shogun of the {{ill|Edo Shogunate|ja|Tokugawa shogunate|1=Tokugawa shogunate|2=ja|3=江戸幕府|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Edo Shogunate|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} (d. {{ill|1866|en|1866|qid=Q7712|lt=1866 AD|1=1866}} ). * {{ill|Meiji era|en|Meiji era|qid=Q3125096|lt=Meiji era|1=Meiji era}} 4th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1871|en|1871|qid=Q7746|lt=1871 AD|1=1871}} {{ill|July 11|en|July 11|qid=Q2701|lt=July 11|1=July 11}} ) – {{ill|Kida Sadakichi|ja|喜田貞吉|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kida Sadakichi|qq=}} , a historian (d. {{ill|1939|en|1939|qid=Q18639|lt=1939 AD|1=1939}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Kan'ei|en|Kan'ei|qid=Q1192913|lt=Kan'ei|1=Kan'ei}} 13th Year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1636|en|1636|qid=Q6885|lt=1636 AD|1=1636}} {{ill|June 27|en|June 27|qid=Q2664|lt=June 27|1=June 27}} ) – {{ill|Date Masamune|en|Date Masamune|qid=Q311183|lt=Date Masamune|1=Date Masamune}} , a military commander and the first lord of the {{ill|Sendai Domain|en|Sendai Domain|qid=Q1062182|lt=Sendai Domain|1=Sendai Domain}} (born {{ill|1567|en|1567|qid=Q6642|lt=1567 AD|1=1567}} ).
